        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Words Matter Act of 2022</strong></p> <p>This bill removes outdated terminology in specified statutes by replacing references to<em> mentally retarded</em> and <em>mental retardation</em> with <em>intellectual disability</em>.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
